      "content": "it’s not that simple though. moving forward feels like just walking into a wall over and over. everything i touch breaks now. i look in the mirror and i don't even see a person, i just see this huge, massive failure. if i go home, i'm just bringing that failure to people who loved me. i feel like the only way to stop the weight is to just... make it stop. all of it. all the noise and the debt and the shame. it just feels like an endless loop of misery.",
